  "response": "\"Wagle Ki Duniya\" is a classic Indian television series that originally aired on Doordarshan in the 1980s. If you're looking to watch all the episodes, here are some potential options:\n\n1. **Doordarshan Archives**  \n   - Doordarshan may have archived episodes of the series. You can check their official website or contact them directly for access.\n\n2. **YouTube**  \n   - Some episodes or clips of \"Wagle Ki Duniya\" are available on YouTube. Users often upload older shows, though the quality and completeness of episodes may vary. Search for playlists or full episodes.\n\n3. **OTT Platforms**  \n   - Platforms like **Shemaroo**, **MX Player**, or **JioCinema** sometimes host classic Indian shows. Check if \"Wagle Ki Duniya\" is available on any of these services.\n\n4. **DVDs**  \n   - Some classic Indian TV series are released on DVDs. Check online retailers like **Amazon India** or **Flipkart** for DVD sets of the show.\n\n5. **Streaming Services**  \n   - Occasionally, platforms like **Hotstar** or **ZEE5** add older shows to their libraries. Keep an eye out for \"Wagle Ki Duniya\" on these services.\n\n6. **Libraries or Cultural Archives**  \n   - Some libraries or cultural organizations in India may have collections of classic Indian television shows. You can inquire at places like the National Film Archive of India or local libraries.\n\nNote: The availability of the show may be limited due to its age. If you're looking for the rebooted version of \"Wagle Ki Duniya\" that aired on Sony SAB in 2021, you can find it on SonyLIV or other streaming platforms.",
